## 🚀 **QUICK START - LIVE DASHBOARD**

### **Professional Dashboard with Live Updates**
```bash
# Navigate to project directory
cd dex_sniping_project

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Set up environment
cp .env.template .env
# Edit .env with your settings

# Start server with live dashboard
uvicorn app.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000 --reload

# Access live dashboard (updating every 10 seconds)
open http://localhost:8000/dashboard
```

### **Watch Live Token Updates**
```bash
# Monitor live console output
# You'll see tokens updating every 10 seconds:
# DOGE2 → WOJAK → DIAMOND → LIQUI → VAULT → SHIBA2 → CHAD...

# Watch main application log
tail -f logs/application/dex_sniper.log

# Watch API calls (tokens updating)
tail -f logs/api/api.log
```

### **Verify Live System**
```bash
# Test live dashboard (should show updating tokens)
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/dashboard
# Returns professional HTML with sidebar and live token cards

# Test live token discovery API (powers the dashboard)
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/tokens/discover?limit=10
# Returns fresh set of 10 tokens each call

# Test dashboard stats API (powers portfolio section)
curl http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/dashboard/stats
# Returns portfolio value, P&L, success rate, etc.

# Expected Health Response:
{
  "status": "healthy",
